official_title: mychoiceTM Implementation in a Real World Clinical Environment - Delivery and Effectiveness
inclusion_criteria:
18 years of age or over

Able to speak and read English

Medical Oncology patients who have had their initial visit

Have a cell phone number and/or an email in the electronic medical record

Exclusion Criteria

Doesn't not speak or read English

Patients who do not have a cancer diagnosis
Healthy volunteers allowed
Must have minimum age of 18 Years
